                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-594-18470201 t18470201-594-punishment-120"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MANNING</hi>—
<rs id="t18470201-594-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
